---
title: Claim Run State Machine
---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> INGESTED : POST /claims\naccepted by API

    INGESTED --> ANALYZING : check_worthy_score >= 0.4\ningestion + detection + entity\nextraction complete

    INGESTED --> CANCELLED : check_worthy_score < 0.4\nclaim not check-worthy

    ANALYZING --> ANALYZING : one or more agents\nstill pending terminal OBX\n(F or X status)

    ANALYZING --> SYNTHESIZED : all 10 agents emitted\nterminal OBX status\nAND synthesizer emitted\nVERDICT F-status

    SYNTHESIZED --> PUBLISHED : edge adapter serialized\nHL7v2 → JSON\nConsumer API persisted verdict

    SYNTHESIZED --> SYNTHESIZED : edge adapter schema\nvalidation failed —\nawaiting investigation

    PUBLISHED --> [*] : terminal state\naudit log retained

    CANCELLED --> [*] : terminal state\naudit log retained

    note right of INGESTED
        ^RUN(run_id, "status") = "INGESTED"
        Run record created.
        Ingestion agent dispatched.
    end note

    note right of ANALYZING
        ^RUN(run_id, "status") = "ANALYZING"
        Orchestrator monitors completion register.
        Parallel fan-out active during this state.
        terminal_obx_count increments per ACK.
    end note

    note right of SYNTHESIZED
        ^RUN(run_id, "status") = "SYNTHESIZED"
        All OBX rows written to YottaDB.
        HL7v2 finalized message complete.
        Edge serialization in progress.
    end note

    note right of PUBLISHED
        ^RUN(run_id, "status") = "PUBLISHED"
        JSON verdict available via Consumer API.
        HL7v2 audit log retained in YottaDB.
        audit_log_ref accessible to consumers.
    end note

    note right of CANCELLED
        ^RUN(run_id, "status") = "CANCELLED"
        Reason recorded in OBX_ROW.
        No agents dispatched beyond
        claim-detector.
    end note
